Installation Instructions
*************************

* Complete install instructions under the /doc folder


Resume :
---------

1) Create a PostgreSQL database from the SQL schema
2) Place "install_files" under the /home/base directory
3) Give read-write access to this files to the Apache user (usaly www or wwwrun)
4) Create the necessary symbolic links

> ln -s /home/base/cgi-bin/archeo /srv/www/cgi-bin
> ln -s /home/base/cgi-bin/archeo/archeo.py /srv/www/cgi-bin/archeo.py

5) manage right for Apache and the database
